SummaryEnglish: When the evil Queen Margarita plans the destruction of peaceful Mikado City. Who will stop her? The city's only hope are five girls in sailor suits, trained in such skills as ramen delivery or useless giggling. Obviously, any all-girl superhero team can cause minor collateral damage, but it takes giant robots for them to really mess things up!
